{{!--
================================================================================
SHIPMAS GRID - 12 Days Card Grid
================================================================================

This partial renders the 12-day countdown grid by fetching posts tagged with
day-1 through day-12.

WHY 12 SEPARATE {{#get}} BLOCKS?
--------------------------------
Ghost's Handlebars {{#get}} helper requires LITERAL filter strings. You cannot
dynamically interpolate values into the filter parameter:

    DOES NOT WORK:
    [#each (range 1 12)]
        [#get "posts" filter="tag:day-[this]"]  <-- Invalid syntax
    [/each]

    ALSO DOES NOT WORK:
    {{#get "posts" filter=(concat "tag:day-" @index)}}  <-- No concat helper

This is a Ghost platform limitation, not a code quality issue. Each day requires
its own explicit {{#get}} block with a hardcoded filter string.

REQUIRED TAGS:
- Each day post needs BOTH tags: "12-days-of-shipmas" AND "day-X" (where X is 1-12)
- The day-X tag controls grid positioning
- Missing days show as "Coming Soon" cards (handled by script.hbs)

CARD STRUCTURE:
- .shipmas-card: Link wrapper with data-day attribute for JS ordering
- .shipmas-card-inner: Flex container for card content
- .shipmas-day-number: Day label badge
- .shipmas-card-image: Feature image or placeholder
- .shipmas-card-content: Title and excerpt

See also: partials/shipmas/script.hbs (handles locked/coming-soon cards)
================================================================================
--}}
